  "detailed_description": "Choose your barbarian character to hack and slash many beasts. A warrior was murdered in the forest west of the mercenary barbarian's camp, now you have to choose one of them and face orcs, giants, cyclops and all kinds of beasts that you will find on your way. Swords and magic will fight alongside you against the beasts to free the kingdom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/513572c4560da49af94346c0cb9ed3e4.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/513572c4560da49af94346c0cb9ed3e4.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/513572c4560da49af94346c0cb9ed3e4.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>THE BATTLE BEGINS<br>Barbarians & Beasts is a beat'em up adventure PC game for 1 to 3 players against the beasts or you can fight against another player in duel mode.<br>This package includes a single file with the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/6c01d317c918e3f96e0607f2cd52f767.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/6c01d317c918e3f96e0607f2cd52f767.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/6c01d317c918e3f96e0607f2cd52f767.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>KILL THE BEASTS<br>Use your keyboard to control the character and slash the enemies to go through 12 stages and win this game.<br>By accumulating points for killing beasts you unlock new characters with a total of 24 male and female warriors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/4ed224138f89bccfad1a5a906096721c.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/4ed224138f89bccfad1a5a906096721c.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/4ed224138f89bccfad1a5a906096721c.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CASTING MAGICS<br>You can use two types of magic, explosion magic and fireballs.<br>Eat mushrooms to launch fireballs and fairy eggs to evoke explosions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/fed476eeb27454deb17862f9489130e2.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/fed476eeb27454deb17862f9489130e2.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/fed476eeb27454deb17862f9489130e2.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>KEYBOARD INSTRUCTIONS:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/279b4e9fdb93fb029d066c95c7abe99f.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=344 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Choose your barbarian character to hack and slash many beasts. A warrior was murdered in the forest west of the mercenary barbarian's camp, now you have to choose one of them and face orcs, giants, cyclops and all kinds of beasts that you will find on your way. Swords and magic will fight alongside you against the beasts to free the kingdom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/513572c4560da49af94346c0cb9ed3e4.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/513572c4560da49af94346c0cb9ed3e4.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/513572c4560da49af94346c0cb9ed3e4.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>THE BATTLE BEGINS<br>Barbarians & Beasts is a beat'em up adventure PC game for 1 to 3 players against the beasts or you can fight against another player in duel mode.<br>This package includes a single file with the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/6c01d317c918e3f96e0607f2cd52f767.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/6c01d317c918e3f96e0607f2cd52f767.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/6c01d317c918e3f96e0607f2cd52f767.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>KILL THE BEASTS<br>Use your keyboard to control the character and slash the enemies to go through 12 stages and win this game.<br>By accumulating points for killing beasts you unlock new characters with a total of 24 male and female warriors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/4ed224138f89bccfad1a5a906096721c.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/4ed224138f89bccfad1a5a906096721c.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/4ed224138f89bccfad1a5a906096721c.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CASTING MAGICS<br>You can use two types of magic, explosion magic and fireballs.<br>Eat mushrooms to launch fireballs and fairy eggs to evoke explosions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/fed476eeb27454deb17862f9489130e2.poster.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/fed476eeb27454deb17862f9489130e2.webm?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/fed476eeb27454deb17862f9489130e2.mp4?t=1761745560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>KEYBOARD INSTRUCTIONS:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695230/extras/279b4e9fdb93fb029d066c95c7abe99f.avif?t=1761745560\" width=614 height=344 /></span>",
